{"tid":661525,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉] 本土政治戰略遊戲「黨爭 - 香港」| 真．通識教育","createTime":"2018-05-11T15:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T13:48:21.000Z","uid":52090,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fc0bd5755f647fadd5900afa586b9fb9062b30c6","tid":661525,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:40:30.000Z","msg":"[拋磚引玉] 本土政治戰略遊戲「黨爭 - 香港」| 真．通識教育<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，咁多位巴打絲打相信唔少人玩「三國志」同「信長之野望」成長，但你有冇諗過「香港」嘅背景隨時比三國同戰國更吸引？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.3gmfw.cn/article/UploadPic/2016-2/201623215025866.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.3gmfw.cn%2Farticle%2FUploadPic%2F2016-2%2F201623215025866.jpg&h=70f0b998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩開「三國志」嘅你，呢一張地圖相信唔會陌生，當初你選擇左邊一個勢力？而今次，係香港，你就要選擇不同政黨！你會選擇小政黨，還時做大台，搶光環？或者為左金錢而出賣香港？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.paopaoche.net/up/2016-1/14541191775780531.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.paopaoche.net%2Fup%2F2016-1%2F14541191775780531.jpg&h=378b1c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個城池都會花費不少時間去設置；而香港嘅城池就係「區議會」，太守就係「區議員」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/m7ewn0q1nffy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fm7ewn0q1nffy.jpg&h=02fdf43b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你每取得一個城池，你就會得到「城池收入」，即係「區議會預算」，你可以將資金收集，等待下一次「選戰」進攻其他城池，或者用作地區工作，增加「民心」。如果「民心」跌至零，不單止會係下次「選戰」失利，更會出現 Revolt，隨時即時下台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pics13.yamedia.tw/41/userfile/s/shikanosengoku/album/15221bec66646a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpics13.yamedia.tw%2F41%2Fuserfile%2Fs%2Fshikanosengoku%2Falbum%2F15221bec66646a.jpg&h=37dfba53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果同其他政黨建立同盟關係，可以好似信長咁建立包圍網，就好似「五區公投」及「飯盒會」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/20/Tinky_Winky_Good.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20071208064542\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F20%2FTinky_Winky_Good.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20071208064542&h=1b51c455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當勢力收入累積一定水平後，可以招賢增加「將領」，或利用政治黑金招募敵對勢力的「將領」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.3gmfw.cn/article/UploadPic/2016-2/20162923358248.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.3gmfw.cn%2Farticle%2FUploadPic%2F2016-2%2F20162923358248.jpg&h=5f81af97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRRUzNiZASIX5UkBTUAVFdFKyxzB0l3LsZin1_6lBcwwZjVjR3f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRRUzNiZASIX5UkBTUAVFdFKyxzB0l3LsZin1_6lBcwwZjVjR3f&h=0c548f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者增加動員力量，同改變意識型態：建制、民主、本土、焦土等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gss0.baidu.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/94cad1c8a786c9173dd71e25c93d70cf3ac757d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.baidu.com%2F9fo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy%2Fzhidao%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F94cad1c8a786c9173dd71e25c93d70cf3ac757d1.jpg&h=026b617a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n意識型態會改變立法會選舉，係立法會議員係政黨中嘅角時正正就係「軍團」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1875000/1877942/0810-LB-table2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1875000%2F1877942%2F0810-LB-table2_1024.jpg&h=2e7d1ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但單程證會每年影響到意識型態，同時會有移民改變生態<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.fxxz.com/up/2010-12/2010122195251108200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.fxxz.com%2Fup%2F2010-12%2F2010122195251108200.jpg&h=c3c59b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想改善單程證問題，可以係立法會提出議案；而立法會每年都會有政改議案，會增加或減低「選戰」難度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/QFO6hCf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQFO6hCf.jpg&h=85cb5f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每隔一段時間，會有突發事件，例如雷曼、歐債、釋法等，每個決定，都會影響深遠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://aamacau.com/files/uploads/2014/09/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E9%A9%85%E6%95%A3%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E3%80%82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamacau.com%2Ffiles%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F09%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E9%25A9%2585%25E6%2595%25A3%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E3%2580%2582.jpg&h=99143a03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會戰上，在野勢力可以利用 Revolt，但風險非常大，會出現警犬打壓，動員力會大減，同時「將領」有機會被捕而被迫退出舞台。<br />\n<br />\n=====================================<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，希望各位可以一齊討論，完善遊戲。（利申：只識吹水，唔識寫Game）"},{"pid":"1b48e492f859851f27685fc149b769825441e7cc","tid":661525,"uid":52090,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果有巴打寫Game，Early Bird 我都會買"},{"pid":"41cf41bc3d03996554bae11a0af42481992399c0","tid":661525,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de75bbe97eff423fdf5da95bf423f521da954c2b","tid":661525,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41cf41bc3d03996554bae11a0af42481992399c0","tid":661525,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7533ce17061b7896cfce2037e6a8f61880e15229","tid":661525,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T17:46:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a326f0cc2d51da2aa88743fc46f9527e28a3028","tid":661525,"uid":52090,"like":0,"d